messages.messageBody:
starznmoongarden: Hi Sandra!! I'm hiding from hurricane Ivan in
Tallahassee....
SandraDodd: How far inland is that?
starznmoongarden: Not much, but apparently we made a good choice because
it's just beyond the reach of the wind and rain.
starznmoongarden: Three hours East of P'cola
starznmoongarden: It's about 30-40 miles inland also

. . . .
starznmoongarden: I packed [the photos] all up...they're in our canopied
truck with all of our cherished keepsakes, our rats and hamsters.

. . . .

Tell everyone we're safe....:)
